<head>IRONY</head><list type="translations"><item xml:lang="zh">反語</item></list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SPEAK so as to INTEND to COMMUNICATE the CONTRARY of what one's WORDS MEAN.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>反語 is the current modern translation word for irony.</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p></div></div>
